com.loyauty.model
Interface LoyautyEnum

All Known Implementing Classes:
Language, Type
public interface LoyautyEnum

All enumerations in GameJab should implement this interface. It defines a method to retrieve the integer value of the enum. Thus, we can deal with enums on the medel level and then persist their integer value in the DB.
